OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FIsrael's prime minister ordered
OL,7,Fattacks on the southern suburbs of
OL,8,FLebanon's capital, a day after ground
OL,9,Fforces reached their deepest point in
OL,10,FBeirut for 26 years.
OL,12,FBenjamin Netanyahu warned "terrorist
OL,13,Ftargets" would be struck as the
OL,14,Fconflict with the Iran-backed armed
OL,15,Fgroup Hezbollah escalated.
OL,17,FIt came as Hezbollah fired rockets at
OL,18,Fnorthern Israel, including the
OL,19,Foutskirts of the coastal city of Haifa.
