PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780413075
OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FIn a joint statement with Defence
OL,7,FMinister Israel Katz on X, formerly
OL,8,FTwitter, Netanyahu said that following
OL,9,F"repeated and ongoing violations" of a
OL,10,FUS-brokered ceasefire, the country's
OL,11,Fmilitary would strike Hezbollah's
OL,12,Fstronghold of Dahieh.
OL,14,FThe Israeli advance presents a
OL,15,Fchallenge in the emerging deal to
OL,16,Fextend the fragile US-Iran war truce.
OL,17,FTehran wants any agreement to end
OL,18,Ffighting to also include Lebanon.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@aO]
