OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780413075
OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FQatar called it a "dangerous
OL,7,Fescalation" and Germany's foreign
OL,8,Fminister said it was cause for serious
OL,9,Fconcern.
OL,11,FIn mid-April, Hezbollah agreed to halt
OL,12,Fattacks on Israel when the ceasefire
OL,13,Fwas signed, but resumed following
OL,14,FIsraeli strikes in Lebanon, which
OL,15,FNetanyahu's government characterised
OL,16,Fas self-defence.
