OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FAfter Monday's warning, large numbers
OL,7,Fof people were seen fleeing Dahiyeh,
OL,8,Fblocking roads leading out of the
OL,9,Fsouthern suburb where Hezbollah enjoys
OL,10,Fwide support.
OL,12,FIsraeli airstrikes overnight on
OL,13,Fsouthern Lebanon left six people dead,
OL,14,Fincluding a Syrian citizen in a
OL,15,Fvillage near the city of Nabatiyeh,
OL,16,Fthe state-run National News Agency
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
