PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780413075
OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Israel's Air Force
OL,7,Fintercepted two projectiles launched
OL,8,Ffrom Lebanon toward Israeli territory,
OL,9,Fas well as a suspicious aerial target
OL,10,Fin the area where Israeli soldiers are
OL,11,Foperating in southern Lebanon. No
OL,12,Finjuries were reported.
OL,14,FHezbollah said it carried out rocket
OL,15,Fand missile attacks on northern Israel
OL,16,Fon Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
