OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FIt came after Israeli troops occupying
OL,7,Fsouthern Lebanon crossed the Litani
OL,8,FRiver to seize the 900-year-old
OL,9,FBeaufort Castle which sits on top of a
OL,10,Fstrategically important ridge.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FKatz said their campaign was not over
OL,18,Fand that they were determined to crush
OL,19,FHezbollah's power.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
