OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FLebanese Prime Minister Nawaf Salam
OL,7,Faccused Israel of pursuing a "scorched-
OL,8,Fearth policy and collective
OL,9,Fpunishment".
OL,11,FHezbollah has rejected direct talks,
OL,12,Fcounting on pressure from Iran, which
OL,13,Fhas demanded an end to the war in
OL,14,FLebanon as part of its talks with
OL,15,FWashington.
