OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FA US official said late on Sunday that
OL,7,FSecretary of State Marco Rubio had
OL,8,Fspoken to Lebanese President Joseph
OL,9,FAoun and Netanyahu to propose a fresh
OL,10,Fpath to continue ongoing negotiations,
OL,11,Fas President Donald Trump weighs a
OL,12,Ftentative ceasefire extension with
OL,13,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
