PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780413075
OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FUnder the proposal, Hezbollah would
OL,7,Fhalt all attacks on Israel and Israel
OL,8,Fwould refrain from escalating military
OL,9,Foperations in the Lebanese capital of
OL,10,FBeirut, according to the official who
OL,11,Fspoke on condition of anonymity to
OL,12,Fdiscuss private diplomatic
OL,13,Fconversations.
OL,15,FThe official said Aoun was open to the
OL,16,Fidea but that Lebanese parliament
OL,17,Fchief Nabih Berri had responded by
OL,18,Fdemanding that Israel first stop all
OL,19,Fmilitary action.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780413075
OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FThey added that the Trump
OL,7,Fadministration does not expect Israel
OL,8,Fto give up retaliating for Hezbollah
OL,9,Fstrikes on its territory.
OL,11,FBerri, a key Hezbollah ally, said in a
OL,12,Fstatement on Sunday that he can
OL,13,Fguarantee the militant group's "full,
OL,14,Fcomprehensive and immediate commitment
OL,15,Fto a ceasefire", adding, "but who will
OL,16,Fforce Israel to stop its aggression?"
OL,18,FAoun added that his government is
OL,19,Fcontinuing work to end "the suffering
OL,20,Fof the Lebanese in general and the
OL,21,Fsoutherners in particular."
