PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780413075
OL,3,CIsrael orders strikes on Beirut's
OL,4,Csouthern suburbs as conflict deepens
OL,6,FAt least 3,412 people have been killed
OL,7,Fin Lebanon, and more than one million
OL,8,Fdisplaced since the start of the war.
OL,10,FIn Israel, Netanyahu sent his
OL,11,F"heartfelt condolences" to the family
OL,12,Fof soldier Sergeant Adam Tzarfati, 20,
OL,13,Fwho was killed in southern Lebanon
OL,14,Fovernight in a drone attack by
OL,15,FHezbollah.
OL,17,FHezbollah's use of hard-to-detect
OL,18,Ffibre optic drones has been deadly for
OL,19,Fthe Israeli military, which is
OL,20,Fstruggling to respond.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@WO]
